episodes.title: through a blue window: The Sullivanians (c)2019 S Feinerman(edited (2020)
episodes.description: In the 1970's, on Manhattan's upper west side, there existed a pyscho sexual therapy group known as the Sullivanian's  In later years characterized as a cult, the therapists advocated patients sleep with the therapists and cut off all contact with their families. Babies were forcibly taken from their mothers.  I was involved for five years. This is my story. (c) 2019 S. feinerman
